  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/internet/\" rel=\"tag\">互联网络</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/19/apple-sends-iwork-for-icloud-beta-invitations-to-everyday-users/\"><img src=\"http://www.blogcdn.com/cn.engadget.com/media/2013/07/iwork-icloud-2.jpg\" style=\"margin: 4px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n苹果在 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/wwdc2013\">WWDC 2013</a> 後很快便开放了针对开发者的 iWork for iCloud <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/06/11/apple-unveils-iwork-for-icloud/\">Beta 测试</a>，现在差不多一个月过去了，他们终于也向普通 iCloud 用户发出了测试邀请。当然，目前的版本并不一定就是最终面市的成品，在接受了大众的「检阅」之后苹果可能还会对其继续做出改进。但不管怎么说，公测开始就代表着正式上线的日子已经不远，大家再多耐心等一等吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/07/19/apple-sends-iwork-for-icloud-beta-invitations-to-everyday-users/\">Engadget</a>、<a href=\"http://www.macrumors.com/2013/07/18/apple-sending-iwork-for-icloud-beta-invites-to-non-developers/\" target=\"_blank\">MacRumors</a><br />\n引用来源：<a href=\"https://www.icloud.com/#iwork\" target=\"_blank\">iCloud.com</a></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/19/apple-sends-iwork-for-icloud-beta-invitations-to-everyday-users/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20670708/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/07/19/apple-sends-iwork-for-icloud-beta-invitations-to-everyday-users/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
